DITECH FINANCIAL, LLC f/k/a Green Tree Servicing, LLC, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Timothy D. GRUNDMANN, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4521 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 23, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The parties' joint stipulation for dismissal filed February 21, 2018, is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is granted. This appeal is dismissed.
